<!-- ════════ HOME ════════ -->
<section class="page-section" id="home">
  <div class="hero">
    <svg class="leaf" style="right:-4%;top:3%;width:52%;opacity:0.06;" viewBox="0 0 500 640" fill="none"><path d="M250 30 C165 65 55 175 45 310 C35 445 115 570 240 580 C365 590 455 470 455 335 C455 200 355 55 250 30Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M250 30 L250 580" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="4"/><path d="M120 155 C165 200 210 210 250 192" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M75 275 C135 305 195 312 250 290" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M85 395 C145 415 205 418 250 398" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M380 155 C335 200 290 210 250 192" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M425 275 C365 305 305 312 250 290" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><ellipse cx="130" cy="185" rx="35" ry="17" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/><ellipse cx="85" cy="308" rx="30" ry="14" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/><ellipse cx="370" cy="185" rx="35" ry="17" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/></svg>
    <svg class="leaf" style="left:-6%;bottom:-8%;width:38%;opacity:0.045;" viewBox="0 0 400 520" fill="none"><path d="M200 25 C125 60 35 165 40 295 C45 425 140 510 245 495 C350 480 415 370 405 245 C395 120 285 25 200 25Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M200 25 L200 495" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="3"/><path d="M95 145 C135 180 170 185 200 168" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M60 260 C112 282 158 286 200 265" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
    <div class="hero-rule"></div>
    <h1>Williamsport's Home for <em>Serious Cigars.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Premium boutique cigars. A lounge worth settling into. Every stick in our humidor was chosen because it earns its place — rare, curated, and worth every dollar.</p>
    <div class="hero-badges">
      <span class="badge-pill">Veteran-Owned</span>
      <span class="badge-pill">Woman-Owned</span>
      <span class="badge-pill">Est. 1977 · New Chapter 2025</span>
      <span class="badge-pill">21 W Church St · Williamsport, PA</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="http://eepurl.com/jEkdTk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">Join the Insider List</a>
      <a href="#thirdrule" class="btn-ghost">The Third Rule →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="value-strip">
    <svg class="leaf" style="right:-1%;bottom:-15%;width:28%;opacity:0.07;" viewBox="0 0 400 520" fill="none"><path d="M200 25 C125 60 35 165 40 295 C45 425 140 510 245 495 C350 480 415 370 405 245 C395 120 285 25 200 25Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M200 25 L200 495" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
    <div class="value-item"><h3>Boutique Only.</h3><p>We don't carry filler brands. Every stick in our humidor was chosen because it earns its place — rare, curated, and worth every dollar.</p></div>
    <div class="value-item"><h3>Concierge Service.</h3><p>Walk in not knowing what you want. Walk out with exactly the right cigar. We'll take you through the humidor personally — no rush, no pressure.</p></div>
    <div class="value-item"><h3>Stay a While.</h3><p>Two big screens. Comfortable seating. Home of the PA Pipe Club, Billtown Chapter. Watch us on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@TheTobaccocenter/" style="color:var(--mint-pale);text-decoration:underline;">YouTube</a> before you even walk in.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="tr-home">
