        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(224,254,248,0.3);margin-top:0.6rem;text-align:center;">The Official Cigar Band — Designed by Jennifer Hogan</p>
      </div>
