<!-- ════════ ABOUT ════════ -->
<section class="page-section" id="about">
  <div class="about-hero">
    <svg class="leaf" style="right:-2%;top:8%;width:38%;opacity:0.09;" viewBox="0 0 500 640" fill="none"><path d="M250 30 C165 65 55 175 45 310 C35 445 115 570 240 580 C365 590 455 470 455 335 C455 200 355 55 250 30Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M250 30 L250 580" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="4"/><path d="M120 155 C165 200 210 210 250 192" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M75 275 C135 305 195 312 250 290" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M85 395 C145 415 205 418 250 398" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><ellipse cx="130" cy="185" rx="35" ry="17" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/><ellipse cx="85" cy="308" rx="30" ry="14" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/></svg>
    <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
    <h1>49 Years of History. <em>A New Chapter.</em></h1>
    <p>The Tobacco Center has been a Williamsport institution since 1977. In 2025, it found its next chapter.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-body">
    <div class="about-main">
      <h2>We Didn't Start a Cigar Shop. We Saved One.</h2>
      <p>The Tobacco Center has been part of Williamsport since 1977 — nearly five decades — going on 50 years of serving the community from 21 W Church Street. When new ownership came in 2025, the goal wasn't to reinvent it. It was to make it everything it always had the potential to be.</p>
      <p><strong>Gray Hogan</strong> is a 100% Permanent &amp; Total Service-Disabled Navy Veteran. He didn't open a cigar shop because it seemed like a good idea — he opened it because he believed Williamsport deserved a lounge that took the craft seriously. One that treated every customer like they belonged there. One worth driving to.</p>
      <p><strong>Jennifer Hogan</strong> brings deep operational experience and a designer's eye to everything from the lounge layout to the brand identity. The space you walk into — the warmth of it, the way it's organized, the way it feels — that's her work.</p>
      <p>Together, they expanded the humidor with boutique brands not found elsewhere in the region, built out a comfortable lounge with two large screens, and established a model built around one thing: knowing their customers by name and knowing what they smoke.</p>
      <p>They opened with a ribbon cutting on Veterans Day, November 11, 2025. That timing wasn't accidental.</p>
      <h2>What "Boutique Only" Actually Means</h2>
      <p>The Tobacco Center does not carry brands to fill space. If a cigar is in the humidor, it earned its place — through quality, through character, through the kind of smoking experience that gives you something to talk about afterward.</p>
      <p>The selection is weighted toward small-batch, artisan producers: LCA releases, RomaCraft, Foundation, Stolen Throne, and others that most shops in the region don't carry at all. When you walk in, you'll find things you haven't tried. That's deliberate. And if you don't know where to start — that's what we're here for.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-card"><h4>Veteran-Owned</h4><p>Gray Hogan served in the United States Navy and is a 100% P&T Service-Disabled Veteran. The Tobacco Center is proud to support Veteran-owned brands and give back to the Veteran community.</p></div>
      <div class="sidebar-card"><h4>Woman-Owned</h4><p>Jennifer Hogan is co-owner and Operations Manager. The Tobacco Center is proud to be a Woman-Owned small business.</p></div>
      <div class="sidebar-card"><h4>Est. 1977</h4><p>Nearly five decades serving Williamsport. New ownership. New energy. Same address.</p></div>
      <div class="sidebar-card"><h4>PA Pipe Club — Billtown Chapter</h4><p>The Tobacco Center is the proud home of the Pennsylvania Pipe Club, Billtown Chapter. Monthly meetings open to all pipe enthusiasts.</p></div>
      <div class="sidebar-card"><h4>Our Private Label</h4><p>The Third Rule — Gray's personal cigar, blended by Karen Berger to his exact specifications. Ask for it by name.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mission-strip">
    <h2>"The tobacconist who cares."</h2>
    <p>tabacarius qui curat — The Tobacco Center · Williamsport, PA</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════ COTM ════════ -->
<section class="page-section" id="cotm">
  <div class="cotm-hero">
    <svg class="leaf" style="right:-2%;bottom:-8%;width:38%;opacity:0.09;" viewBox="0 0 500 640" fill="none"><path d="M250 30 C165 65 55 175 45 310 C35 445 115 570 240 580 C365 590 455 470 455 335 C455 200 355 55 250 30Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M250 30 L250 580" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="4"/><path d="M120 155 C165 200 210 210 250 192" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M75 275 C135 305 195 312 250 290" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M85 395 C145 415 205 418 250 398" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><ellipse cx="130" cy="185" rx="35" ry="17" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/></svg>
    <span class="eyebrow">Cigar of the Month Club</span>
    <h1>Exclusive Membership. <em>No Exceptions.</em></h1>
    <p>A monthly flight of hand-selected premium and rare cigars — curated by Gray, picked up on the 1st. Membership is capped. Exclusivity is the point.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cotm-perks">
    <svg class="leaf" style="left:-2%;bottom:-12%;width:28%;opacity:0.07;" viewBox="0 0 400 520" fill="none"><path d="M200 25 C125 60 35 165 40 295 C45 425 140 510 245 495 C350 480 415 370 405 245 C395 120 285 25 200 25Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M200 25 L200 495" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
    <div class="perk"><h4>Monthly Selection</h4><p>4–5 premium cigars every month — including exclusive LCA drops, boutique releases, and limited-run sticks you won't find anywhere else. Box pickup the first Friday of every month.</p></div>
    <div class="perk"><h4>10% Member Discount</h4><p>As a COTM member, you get 10% off all tobacco purchases in-store. Every visit. Every stick. Whether you're stocking up or trying something new.</p></div>
    <div class="perk"><h4>Members' Discovery Box</h4><p>Our community humidor is stocked with rotating rare and classic cigars — free for members to enjoy in the lounge. Try one or leave a stick for a fellow member.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cotm-selection">
    <span class="eyebrow dark-teal">May 2026 Selection</span>
    <h2>The Boutique Powerhouse Collection</h2>
    <p>A masterclass in modern boutique blending — high-scoring releases from Stolen Throne and Foundation, alongside exclusive LCA drops representing the new school of tobacco.</p>
    <div class="cigar-grid">
      <div class="cigar-card"><h3>Stolen Throne Crook of the Crown</h3><div class="cigar-meta">The Flagship</div><p>Rich and complex. Heavy notes of dark chocolate, earth, and creamy spice. One of the most talked-about boutique releases of the year.</p></div>
      <div class="cigar-card"><h3>LCA Year of Ed</h3><div class="cigar-meta">Aged 2 Years · Limited</div><p>Jalapa Habano wrapper with a Salvadoran binder. Aged two years before release. Deep wood, leather, and a long, satisfying finish.</p></div>
      <div class="cigar-card"><h3>LCA The G.O.A.T.</h3><div class="cigar-meta">The LCA Original</div><p>The cigar that started it all for LCA. Superbly balanced with a clean, refined finish. A must-smoke for any boutique fan.</p></div>
      <div class="cigar-card"><h3>Foundation El Güegüense</h3><div class="cigar-meta">The Heroine · Connecticut Broadleaf</div><p>One of the most decorated cigars of the past decade. Connecticut Broadleaf maduro with dark fruit, cocoa, and cedar. A modern classic.</p></div>
      <div class="cigar-card"><h3>Tradecraft Azorian Corona Gorda</h3><div class="cigar-meta">The Standout Vitola</div><p>Highlights the blend's natural sweetness, toasted nuts, and subtle floral spice. An unexpected favorite every time.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cotm-cta">
    <svg class="leaf" style="right:-2%;top:-5%;width:32%;opacity:0.07;" viewBox="0 0 500 640" fill="none"><path d="M250 30 C165 65 55 175 45 310 C35 445 115 570 240 580 C365 590 455 470 455 335 C455 200 355 55 250 30Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M250 30 L250 580" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="4"/></svg>
    <span class="eyebrow">Ready to Join?</span>
    <h2>Membership is <em>$50 a Month.</em></h2>
    <p>Membership is exclusive and capped. When the club is full, we maintain a waitlist. The best time to get on the list is now.</p>
    <a href="http://eepurl.com/jEkdTk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">Get on the List</a>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-ghost">Call Us to Join</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════ EVENTS ════════ -->
<section class="page-section" id="events">
  <div class="events-hero">
    <svg class="leaf" style="right:-2%;top:0;width:38%;opacity:0.1;" viewBox="0 0 500 640" fill="none"><path d="M250 30 C165 65 55 175 45 310 C35 445 115 570 240 580 C365 590 455 470 455 335 C455 200 355 55 250 30Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M250 30 L250 580" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="4"/><path d="M120 155 C165 200 210 210 250 192" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M75 275 C135 305 195 312 250 290" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M85 395 C145 415 205 418 250 398" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="2.5"/><ellipse cx="130" cy="185" rx="35" ry="17" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/><ellipse cx="85" cy="308" rx="30" ry="14" fill="none" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="1.8"/></svg>
    <span class="eyebrow">Lounge Events</span>
    <h1>Something's Always <em>Happening.</em></h1>
    <p>The lounge isn't just a place to smoke. It's a place to show up. Regulars, new faces, and the occasional great movie — all welcome.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="events-grid">

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Movie Mondays · 6–9 PM</div>
      <h3>Movie Mondays</h3>
      <p>A classic film, a great cigar, and good company. Every Monday in the lounge, 6–9 PM.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>My Cousin Vinny <span class="date">Mon, May 4</span></li>
        <li>Ocean's Eleven <span class="date">Mon, May 11</span></li>
        <li>Best in Show <span class="date">Mon, May 18</span></li>
        <li>Saving Private Ryan <span class="date">Mon, May 25</span></li>
        <li>Nobody <span class="date">Mon, Jun 1</span></li>
        <li>Indiana Jones &amp; the Last Crusade <span class="date">Mon, Jun 8</span></li>
        <li>Beverly Hills Cop <span class="date">Mon, Jun 15</span></li>
        <li>48 Hours <span class="date">Mon, Jun 22</span></li>
        <li>Nobody 2 <span class="date">Mon, Jun 29</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Monthly · First Friday</div>
      <h3>COTM Club Box Day</h3>
      <p>The first Friday of every month, Cigar of the Month Club members pick up their new selection. Stop in, see what's in the box, and stay for a smoke. Not a member? Ask us about the list.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>May Box Pickup <span class="date">Fri, May 1</span></li>
        <li>June Box Pickup <span class="date">Fri, Jun 5</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Limited Release · First Friday</div>
      <h3>LCA / Privada First Friday Release</h3>
      <p>Exclusive limited cigar releases drop on the first Friday of the month — available in-store only while supplies last. These go fast. Get on the Insider List to be notified first.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>Privada LCA Release <span class="date">Fri, May 1</span></li>
        <li>LCA First Friday Release <span class="date">Fri, Jun 5</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Monthly · 7 PM</div>
      <h3>Poker Night</h3>
      <p>Shuffle up and deal. Monthly poker nights in the lounge — cigars encouraged, good attitude required. 7 PM sharp.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>Poker Night <span class="date">Thu, May 14</span></li>
        <li>Poker Night <span class="date">Thu, Jun 11</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Monthly · 2–5 PM</div>
      <h3>PA Pipe Club — Billtown Chapter</h3>
      <p>The Tobacco Center is the proud home of the Pennsylvania Pipe Club, Billtown Chapter. Monthly meetings open to all pipe enthusiasts — bring your pipe, try something from the tin selection, and connect with fellow smokers.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>Pipe Club Meeting <span class="date">Sun, May 24</span></li>
        <li>Pipe Club Meeting <span class="date">Sun, Jun 14</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Members Only · Wednesday</div>
      <h3>The Palate Clinic</h3>
      <p>A guided cigar tasting experience limited to 10 guests — The Exclusive 10. A deep dive into wrapper comparisons, vitola education, and premium boutique selections. Reserve your seat by calling or stopping in.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>Palate Clinic · Seats Limited <span class="date">Wed, May 21</span></li>
        <li>Palate Clinic · Seats Limited <span class="date">Wed, Jun 17</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Jun 20 · Starting at Noon</div>
      <h3>Pappy's Cigar Box Unveiling &amp; Avowed Event</h3>
      <p>A special collaboration event with our partner Harry Entz of Pappy's Cigar Box LLC and Avowed Cigars. Join us for the big unveiling starting at noon — this one is not to be missed.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>Pappy's Unveiling &amp; Avowed Event <span class="date">Sat, Jun 20 · Noon</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="event-card">
      <div class="event-day">Always Open</div>
      <h3>The Lounge</h3>
      <p>No event required. Pull up a chair, pick a great cigar, and stay as long as you like. Two screens. Coffee. Good company.</p>
      <ul class="event-list">
        <li>Mon – Thu <span class="date">9 AM – 7 PM</span></li>
        <li>Fri – Sat <span class="date">9 AM – 8 PM</span></li>
        <li>Sunday <span class="date">Closed</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>>

  <div class="events-note">
    <svg class="leaf" style="right:0;bottom:-8%;width:22%;opacity:0.08;" viewBox="0 0 400 520" fill="none"><path d="M200 25 C125 60 35 165 40 295 C45 425 140 510 245 495 C350 480 415 370 405 245 C395 120 285 25 200 25Z" fill="#4dbf8a"/><path d="M200 25 L200 495" stroke="#4dbf8a" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
    <p>Events are posted on <strong>Facebook (@TheTobaccoCenter)</strong> and on the events board inside the lounge. Follow along so you don't miss a thing.</p>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/TheTobaccoCenter/" class="btn-primary">Follow on Facebook</a>
  </div>
</section>

